header.gameNote: BASKETBALL HALL OF FAME TIP-OFF - CAMPUS GAME

videos.description: Jordan Poole crosses up his defender and throws a sweet wraparound pass to Charles Matthews, who finishes with a reverse layup.
videos.headline: Poole throws razzle-dazzle assist to Matthews

videos.description: Jordan Poole runs the screen-and-roll with Jon Teske, who ends up with a wide-open lane and finishes with authority.
videos.headline: Teske throws down two-handed jam

videos.description: Austin Davis misses the front end of a 1-and-1, but steals the ball for a layup after Norfolk State forgets that it's a live ball.
videos.headline: Norfolk State falls asleep on 1-and-1

videos.description: Armani Branch tries to finish with a finger roll, but Isaiah Livers chases him down and swats it away off the glass.
videos.headline: Livers glasses Branch for huge rejection

videos.description: Xavier Simpson pushes in transition and throws a no-look pass to Charles Matthews, who puts down a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Simpson finds Matthews on fast break

videos.description: Eli Brooks whips a pass to Jon Teske, who throws down a two-handed slam on Nic Thomas.
videos.headline: Teske ends first half with thunderous jam

videos.description: Isaiah Livers finds freshman Ignas Brazdeikis, who challenges a Norfolk State defender and hammers it down with two hands.
videos.headline: Brazdeikis double clutches for big slam

videos.description: Wolverine freshman Ignas Brazdeikis spins his way to the bucket and finishes a layup through contact.
videos.headline: Brazdeikis spins for and-1
